      "content": "it's not just \"difficult moments.\" it's everything. i spent 10 years on this. my entire identity was tied to that company. now i'm just this guy who owes millions to people who don't care about my excuses. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize myself. it's like there's just nothing left to go back to. everything i worked for is a lie.",
